node.text:
If you have been with me for awhile then you know I have shared my stories of being bullied when I was a child. Even today online I am still pushed around by people who want to humiliate and intimidate me. It is painful. But I am also grateful for having gone through these challenges because now stronger than ever I can share my story with others with the hopes to stop bullying. @drshaheem YOU ARE A GEM 💎 thank you for knowledge and guidance as we navigate through life. You have done so much work in the arena of anti-bullying and I am grateful for your support. Parents. I hope you find a moment to listen to her and this session. It will change your children’s lives. 
🦋 our pick-up event for today the book is now FULL. You can pre- order the book and doll on my website www.SHALLZ..com
So grateful for your love
And support

node.text:
A few years ago after I decided to write a book I had the idea to find the illustrator through a search on social media. I received hundreds and hundreds of emails. Having a hard time picking someone I mentioned to my mom I was struggling and wish I could give everyone a chance. And that’s when everything changed. She told me I have a cousin in Iran who is an incredible artist and could possibly do it. 
And she did. We haven’t sent each other in more than 4 decades. She is my family. My cousin. And now the illustrator of my first book. 
@azi.cake1 I LOVE YOU! Thank you for helping me make my dreams come true. I pray for the day I can hold you and squeeze you again. 
ASHEGETAM AZI jooooon! 🦋
Today is the final day to pre-order you book and pick it up at a special event in SOCAL. Order yours at www.SHALLZ.com

NEW SESSION And a must watch! 
Who are emotional vampires? Are they part of some strange cult or horror movie? Unfortunately not - many live amongst us! They are called emotional vampires because their actions and attitudes tend to drain the emotional energy out of different people they come in contact with. They can be psychologically exhausting due to their need for constant attention and crisis. Join me and Dr. Shaheem on this segment as we discuss ways to better understand them and establish boundaries to protect our own emotional well-being 🧠🧛🏻‍♂️ @drshaheem #morethanmind #mentalhealth 
🎧 you can also find segment on my YouTube channel. And take us on the go via audio version on my podcast channel.

🦋🐛
Growing up wasn’t easy. The memories of being bullied and called names still stings at times. I didn’t fit it. It was hard to make friends. But as I look back now I realize I was on my own journey to find my wings and fly. 
I hope the story of Myla brings love and light to all your homes. I hope it calms a young child, inspires a teen, or connects with an adult who still feels alone today. 

Pre-orders for My New Book ‘Myla Caterpillars become Butterflies’ begin this Thursday morning. You can also buy the Myla doll as a set. If you live in Southern California you have the option to skip the shipping charges and pick up your book and MYLA doll at a special book signing event in August. 
All the magic starts this Thursday Morning and you can find all the information soon at www.SHALLZ.com
You will meet the illustrator of this book and learn about the ladies who helped me put this book together in July 🦋
#shallz #newbook #myla #caterpillarsbecomebutterflies #childrensbook #ididit

node.text: 1️⃣6️⃣ years since one of the best days of my life. Behrooz Joon. Can you believe this was 16 years ago on this very day? Look at us. So young. So in love. So ready to start our lives together. We have  laughed. We have cried. We have been knocked down. We have held onto each other and got right back up. We brought 4 beautiful souls into this world and I am so incredible grateful for you and our family. What was. Still is. Always and forever my Brucie you will be 💗 here’s to another 100 years of annoying you 🤣 I love you. Happy anniversary 💗 #anniversary #16years #thisisus

Myla. Are you ready? Time for you to go home with some families and work your magic. 
For those who pre-ordered you books several months ago I am waiting for you at this special private event just for you. 
✨For anyone else who orders their book in the next few weeks all profits from my new book will be sent to young women and children in Afghanistan who need their wings to fly. Myla are you ready??? 🦋💜🦋✨#myfirstbook #myla #notobullying 
A special thank you @bel_events for setting up the most magical space for us to meet. And to @sweetlilisbakery for hosting me at their bakery. 
And lastly to my girls @beautybymelina @azi_fairysecret turning this mama who has not slept into a butterfly today 🦋

My dearest husband, it is your birthday today. I wanted to wish you the very best, but you already have me. No need 🤣🤣🤣

My Brucie. I know you aren’t the biggest fan of celebrating your birthday but I want to spoil the man who stole my ❤️. The man who shows up for our family everyday. The best daddy who adores his kids. The man with a heart of gold and one of the kindest people I know. And not to mention the man who puts up with me everyday 😉 I love growing old with you. Happy birthday to my Brucie. May all your dreams and wishes come true 🥳 #birthdayboy #happybirthday
